Lidar Manual

How to use Lidar and use Hector_Slam 
Follow this direction

 Execute $cd catkin_ws/
 Execute $roscore
 Don’t close this terminal
 Open new the second terminal
 Execute this $cd catkin_ws/ on the new terminal
 Execute this $ ls -l /dev | grep ttyUSB command to check ttyUSB0
 Execute $ sudo chmod 666 /dev/ttyUSB0
 Execute $ source devel/setup.bash
 Execute $ roslaunch rplidar_ros rplidar.launch
 Don’t close the second terminal
 Open new the thrid terminal
 Execute this $cd catkin_ws/ on the new terminal
 Execute this $ ls -l /dev | grep ttyUSB command to check ttyUSB0
 Execute $ sudo chmod 666 /dev/ttyUSB0
 Execute $ source devel/setup.bash
 Execute $ roslaunch hector_slam_launch tutorial.launch 
  

